 Nollywood actress and politician, Funke Akindele has lost her mother. The actress’ older sister Olubunmi Akindele announced the death in a statement on Tuesday. READ ALSO: Funke Akindele Recounts How Saddest Day Of Her Life Almost Ruined ‘Battle On Bukka Street’ The statement read: “It is with heavy hearts, but in total submission to God Almighty that the ADEBANJO and AKINDELE families announce the passing of their daughter, mother, grandmother and sister, DR. R B ADEBANJO-Akindele, which occurred on Tuesday 07 February 2023. May her gentle soul begin its rest eternal in peace. Amen. Obsequies in honour of her passing shall be announced in due course.”